# HTML5/CSS3 Template Collection

A collection of web templates showcasing modern front-end techniques.

## Templates

### `/templates/lp/` — Modern Landing Page
A full-featured SaaS landing page built with Vite + Tailwind CSS v4.
Uses CSS Scroll-driven Animations, View Transitions API, Container Queries,
and variable fonts. See `templates/lp/README.md` for details.

### Legacy Template (root files)
The original HTML5/CSS3 template (index.html, css/, js/, img/).
